over there as a dormitory. And boys would be 
sticking out, looking at that, and just as sure as

14:57.576 --> 15:12.681
they had one of those, one of those boys would 
presumably fall out a window. They'd take their

15:12.781 --> 15:18.270
dummy and dress him up, and when they got down to the 
right point, they'd push him out. And finally, I

15:18.571 --> 15:21.476
break up that damn chance. As

